<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= language === 'zh' ? 'zh-TW' : 'en' %>">
<head>
<!-- meta attributes -->
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="author" content="Jack Gowan">
<meta name="description" content="first built maze">
<title>The Maze - Upward Flight</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/a_maze_style.css">
</head>
<body>
<h1 class="main-title"><%= translations?.[language]?.title || 'Upward Flight' %></h1>

  <div class="room-container">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="room-image">
        <img src="/images/a3_maze-hide-stairs.png" alt="Upward flight from the creature">
      </div>
      <div class="room-content">
        <div class="room-text">
          <code>
            <%- translations?.[language]?.text || `<p>You burst through a doorway into a vast chamber. Moonlight! Blessed moonlight streams through cracks in a collapsed ceiling high above. Fresh air fills your lungs.</p>
            <p>You are all alone.</p>
             <p>You're in what appears to be an ancient temple chamber. Moonlight illuminates the room. </p>
             <p>You could use your strength to climb up towards the moonlight and fresh air - an escape route to freedom. To your right, an intact corridor descends back into the maze's depths, lit by strange phosphorescent fungi.</p>
            <p style="font-weight: bold;">Do you seek escape or continue exploring?</p>` %>
          </code>
        </div>

        <hr/>

        <div class="navigation">
          <p><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.prompt || 'Choose your path:' %></p>
          <a href="/maze/escape-no-secret"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[0] || 'Escape the maze through the moonlight ceiling' %></a>
          <a href="/maze/sword-explore"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[1] || 'Go deeper into the Maze' %></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
